<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6758533>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Diaeretellus nymphaealis sp. nov. Female: (a) head; (b) mesoscutum; (c) propodeum; (d) petiole; (e) ovipositor sheaths; (g) fore wing. (f) Male genitalia." ;
